{"type": "article", "id": 84, "title": "日本人是不会放过乔布斯的，热血漫画连载一", "description": "近日，日本两名漫画家联手创作了一套以苹果公司早期创业史为蓝本的连载漫画 Steves 。这部走热血喜剧路线的作品以史蒂夫·乔布斯和史蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克为主角，将会于6 月 27 日登上由日本小学馆发行的漫画集刊物 《Big Comic Superior》。现在它已经放出了早期初版，迫不及待的读者们可以前往下载阅读之", "date": "2014-05-05T09:44:36Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 184, "name": "乔布斯"}, {"id": 232, "name": "连载漫画"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}], "category": 3, "column": null, "author": 8, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607140306DXVq5b1cMx40nuGd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，日本两名漫画家联手创作了一套以苹果公司早期创业史为蓝本的<a href=\"http://www.cultofmac.com/275790/apples-early-years-gets-manga-treatment-new-comic-series/\">连载漫画</a> Steves 。这部走热血喜剧路线的作品以史蒂夫·乔布斯和史蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克为主角，将会于6 月 27 日登上由日本小学馆发行的漫画集刊物 《Big Comic Superior》。现在它已经放出了早期初版，迫不及待的读者们可以前往<a href=\"http://p.booklog.jp/book/28287\">下载</a>阅读之。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t漫画作者小沢高広様和妹尾朝子様表示，即在小学馆连载后漫画或于年内推出单行本，而关于漫画的更多信息可关注其<a href=\"http://twitter.com/STEVES_info\" target=\"_blank\">Twitte</a>r账号。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140257TOui2C54XesadoEb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140257fObwGrQCShJj8dAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140258EJ9hwgUBAOiX2TLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140259KYZTw4voMCJqGWBp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140259jvWBLtYkMnKciGgx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140300awDCdiQ2E0vMFI9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140300rtFkHhy3QMiDNsvx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140301SI7awGLyuiZN01OK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140301Sjzcw2eWit49sfdI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140302SzfgHteUX3D5NhrW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140302mYSDK4HPWT2wNiM8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140303fIYo2mGPNdhJDKAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140304nYpfPuUlNFqRQVKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071403049Vi105KRglDnU3hG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140305Wa3LgAVwx9mzPOeK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140305g0Z7MUJEO2Sd8xeu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140306RvGILJixA75mt0dn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来自<a href=\"http://p.booklog.jp/book/28287\">pubooパブー</a> \r\n</p>\r\n图片翻译：戒子\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}